title: My Life is Worth Something Too: thoughts from a young singers life
description: This collection of songs and poetry is a tale of my life, you can even call it my journey and it all began when I was around 18 and the book ends where my life is now as a young strong woman who finally dared to reach for the stars. Among these pages are a lot of emotions and growth and I am told that they reach your soul.
author: Line F. Nielsen
